OL,3,CWarning of widespread disruption in
OL,4,Chealth service
OL,6,FPatients have been warned that the
OL,7,Fhealth service in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwill experience "widespread
OL,9,Fdisruption" next week when junior
OL,10,Fdoctors embark on a two-day strike.
OL,12,FThe statement from the Department of
OL,13,FHealth came ahead of the first of two
OL,14,Fplanned 48-hour walkouts by junior
OL,15,Fdoctors, which will start at 7am on
OL,16,FWednesday. The second strike is
OL,17,Fschedule for June 6-8.
