OL,6,FJunior doctors in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Ftook strike action for the first time
OL,8,Fin March, staging a 24-hour walkout
OL,9,Fthat affected hospitals and GP
OL,10,Fsurgeries.
OL,12,FThe strike action was called after
OL,13,F97.6% of junior doctors balloted by
OL,14,Ftheir union, BMA Northern Ireland,
OL,15,Fvoted in favour of industrial action.
