OL,3,CWarning of widespread disruption in
OL,4,Chealth service
OL,6,FThe BMA has called for a commitment to
OL,7,Fa full pay restoration to 2008 levels,
OL,8,Fclaiming that junior doctors have seen
OL,9,Ftheir salaries effectively eroded by
OL,10,F30% over the last 15 years due to a
OL,11,Ffailure to make pay awards in line
OL,12,Fwith inflation.
OL,14,FThe union has said some newly
OL,15,Fqualified doctors are earning #13 per-
OL,16,Fhour in Northern Ireland.
OL,18,FThe department said health trusts
OL,19,Fwould be working to mitigate the
OL,20,Fimpact as much as possible.
