OL,6,FIt said more information on affected
OL,7,Fservice areas would be published next
OL,8,Fweek.
OL,10,F"Significant disruption is expected
OL,11,Fnot only on the two strike days but
OL,12,Fover following days," said the
OL,13,Fstatement.
OL,15,F"The department stands ready to
OL,16,Fcontinue discussions with the Junior
OL,17,FDoctors Committee and does not accept
OL,18,Fthat talks have 'collapsed'.
