OL,6,F"There are important issues of
OL,7,Fsubstance to be progressed, including
OL,8,Freform of the current junior doctor
OL,9,Fcontract in NI. The department has
OL,10,Foffered a process of independent
OL,11,Farbitration, but this has not been
OL,12,Ftaken up to date.
OL,14,F"When the ballot for industrial action
OL,15,Fwas launched, junior doctors ` like
OL,16,Fthe rest of the NI health service
OL,17,Fstaff ` had received no pay award for
OL,18,F2023/24.
