OL,6,F"That is no longer the case. The 2023/
OL,7,F24 recommendations of the national pay
OL,8,Freview body, the DDRB, have now been
OL,9,Fimplemented in NI. The award will be
OL,10,Fpaid in the June pay run, landing in
OL,11,Fpay packets next month.
OL,13,F"For junior doctors in Northern
OL,14,FIreland, it will bring an average pay
OL,15,Fincrease of 9.07%, with those in their
OL,16,Ffirst year receiving a 10.68% uplift.
