OL,6,F"The department cannot resolve the BMA
OL,7,Fdemand for pay restoration ` for a pay
OL,8,Fsettlement that reverses public sector
OL,9,Fpay limits over the past decade and
OL,10,Fmore.
OL,12,F"That's an issue that has impacted
OL,13,Fpublic sector employees across the UK
OL,14,Fas a result of UK Government policy.
OL,15,FIt is a national issue that cannot be
OL,16,Fresolved locally."
