OL,6,FThe BMA's Northern Ireland Junior
OL,7,FDoctor Committee said newly qualified
OL,8,Fmedics in Northern Ireland see
OL,9,Fcolleagues working elsewhere in the UK
OL,10,Fand in other jurisdictions getting
OL,11,Fbetter pay and conditions for less
OL,12,Fpressurised workloads.
OL,14,FIt has warned that doctors are leaving
OL,15,Fthe health service in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fin increasing numbers due to
OL,17,F"decreasing morale from poor pay and
OL,18,Fhigh workloads".
